fact of vanilla radiance cascades. We'll do this with the approximate versi=
on of <code>vec3(2.2)</code> when reading and <code>vec3(1.0 / 2.2)</code> =
when writing. Ths reason behind this is WebGL uses sRGB and we want to work=
